org.sxb.kit.io

クラス AbstractResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sxb.kit.io.AbstractResource
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    InputStreamSource, Resource
    直系の既知のサブクラス:
    AbstractFileResolvingResource, ByteArrayResource, InputStreamResource, VfsResource

    public abstract class AbstractResource
extends java.lang.Object
implements Resource
    Convenience base class for Resource implementations, pre-implementing typical behavior.

    The "exists" method will check whether a File or InputStream can be opened; "isOpen" will always return false; "getURL" and "getFile" throw an exception; and "toString" will return the description.

    導入されたバージョン:
    28.12.2003
    作成者:
    Juergen Hoeller

      • contentLength

        public long contentLength()
                   throws java.io.IOException
        This implementation reads the entire InputStream to calculate the content length. Subclasses will almost always be able to provide a more optimal version of this, e.g. checking a File length.
        定義:
        contentLength インタフェース内 Resource
        例外:
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if InputStreamSource.getInputStream() returns null.
        java.io.IOException - if the resource cannot be resolved (in the file system or as some other known physical resource type)
        関連項目:
        InputStreamSource.getInputStream()
